Introduction

ShuHua is a Taiwanese singer and model under Cube Entertainment. She is the visual and maknae of the girl group (G)I-DLE. She used to be a model before debuting as an idol under Cube. Shuhua debuted as a member of (G)I-DLE on May 2, 2018, with their mini-album "I Am" and the title song "Latata".

In 2017, She appeared on 10cm's 'PET' MV. She was also recently announced as Colorgram's muse on March 15, 2023.

On February 8, 2024, CUBE Entertainment announced that Shuhua would take a break from activities due to health issues, but she resumed activities on March 21, 2024.
